  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.netbeans.jemmy.Outputable, org.netbeans.jemmy.Timeoutable

    public class NewProjectWizardOperator
extends WizardOperator
    Handles NetBeans New Project wizard and its components Categories and Projects. It is invoked from main menu File -> New Project...
    Usage: 
      NewProjectWizardOperator npwop = NewProjectWizardOperator.invoke();
  npwop.selectCategory("Standard");
  npwop.selectProject("Java Application");
  npwop.next();
  npwop.getDescription();
